                    { "IQA0176", "Mandatory", "Checkbox", null, "4", "B", "IQT0015", "A final report should be submitted to the Research Ethics Committee (REC) within 12 months of the end of the project, including a public summary of results. How else do you intend to report and disseminate the results of the project? Select all that apply:", "Look-up list", null, null },
