                    { "IQA0179", "Mandatory", "Boolean", null, "6", "B", "IQT0015", "You should enable the sharing of study data, with appropriate safeguards in place, to other interested groups and communities. Sharing data maximises and respects the contribution of participants and enables and supports further re-use. Do you plan to share de-identified individual participant-level data?", "Boolean", null, null },
